data.description: HOME IS WHERE THE HEART IS...CHECK OUT THIS PERFECT STARTER HOME! GREAT OPPORTUNITY FOR FIRST-TIME HOME BUYERS! Look no further than this beautiful home located in one of South Tuscaloosa's most popular areas. This 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath Home features split bedrooms with a nice open floor plan. Walk into your future home from a covered porch and into the living area, highlighted by beautiful hardwoods and vaulted ceilings.  The Master is accentuated with a trey ceiling and brand new carpet, with a large master bath, separate soaking tub and shower with a walk-in closet.  The open kitchen features tons of counter space and cabinets, a farmhouse sink with stainless steel appliances, and a kitchen bar. Located in close proximity to shopping, restaurants, schools, and recreation. Just off HWY 69 South, your future home is minutes from the University of Alabama, downtown Tuscaloosa, and the Amphitheater. WELCOME HOME!
